i've only got my internet on the 2nd or 3rd day after i reached the campus...cos of those admin stuffs u noe la....haiz....other than tat i'm damn sianz....the room is to enclosed...really can't stand it...couldn't sleep well for the first few nites...partly jetlag...partly miss home...watever...it's juz not a gd feeling then...it's as if u r all alone in tis world despite havin sum frens and neighbours ard....

will do a more detailed update next blog k...when i'm really free and hav tons of time...not tat i'm very bz haha...

and mum hav been calling me everyday =)...it's ex...but it's needed for the first few days and so...hopefully can get a webcam...shall see...

take care ppl!

finally trial and error as u guided yappy...i'm more or less done...but still haven reach max satisfaction keke...and to tink tat i spent the whole morning doin it....keke...a bit wasting time i noe...=p...but since i'll be slacking at home all the time now...eh...not suppose to...but wif my aunt and cousin (who's having chicken pox haiz) still spending some time over here wif us, i'm very prone to being lazy to do my own things...tat's y there's nothin accomplished...and ge exam coming in another 2 weeks time oh damn....wat hav i learnt...abstract...haiz...how to study man?!?!?! and i've to wait till aunt n cousin go back before i can meet up wif friends...cos it doesn't seem nice and mum's still goin for work....hopefully wdl class gathering is goin to make it...oops i sound a bit pessimistic...and hopefully it's goin to be at sentosa...can hav some fun again...and new year's eve...eh jea i still haven ask...giv a few more days k...
whenever it comes to hols i really dunno wat to do....nvm =p

cool...i'm taken into the rock world again by SLY with "It's my life"!!! although i oso like RnB, i guess it's only the chinese RnB singers r attracting me...SLY still ROCKS...glad tat he's cutting an album too!!! but tink i would prefer him performing LIVE =)
so it doesn't matter who wins....
anyway sth very contradicting...u shld noe i hate tat sun ho...and i'm somehow anti-christian person...but SLY is from City Harvest...a christian...haiz...

yeah! the pressurizing period gonna be over soon...with one last paper tis afternoon...cool!
how long hav i been waiting...erm...well can't trace back anymore...
out of a sudden i seem to hav lotz of free time which i can't plan how to use it...but i better use it meaningfully and not waste it...
yesterday i was actually gazing at the clock tat's right in front of me during the last half hour of bf322 paper..counting down to mark the end of my 'misery'...hahaz...i'm simply not disciplined enough to study tat much for it..
yesterday was really a tough day juz like 2nd of nov...but i hav survived thru keke...the only thing to worry is the ultimate result which i guess isn't of priorty concern to me anymore...i oso dunno y...i can only pray tat dun let mi fail any...or my course structure will be messed up for sure
and becos i was so tired, i actually allow myself to seat behind a couple for a ride home...and i tried to pretend my absence but my fren tried to engage me in talking...in the end i still reach home quite late, cos they nvr send me str home but a few mrt stations away...and tired as i was, i took bus home for the first time since tis semester...i tink so...my laziness is starting to crawl in again as holiday is starting...i'm looking forward to it...looking forward to some fun and hopefully some work experience...and i'm oso looking forward to Ontario...but i'm oredi starting to worry about my family esp my sis and bro who nvr failed to make mum angry....haiz....
i'm looking forward to sitex, so i can get a good-for-value digi cam...cos tat one has been spoilt for a long lasting year...wanna capture a whole lot of moments...
looking forward to sentosa chalet (which clash wif JAY's concert and glad tat i've seem to find new owner for the ticket), cos i gonna be the programmer for the family gathering...and i dun hav to play at all *_*
kk...gonna study some bits to make myself feel comfortable goin into the exam hall...till then either 

good luck for ur upcoming exams OR
happy working OR
enjoy your holidays OR
enjoy dating with your boiboi =)

just to share one of my enjoyments...

at this point of time, the rain has juz stopped. and it's when the cooling breeze is coming for you...feel its gentleness and coolness which actually brings warmth to ur heart...dun hav to get a cup of freshly brewed coffee, but can't lack a song to accompany tis kind of weather and feeling...with the correct music in place, everything will be at ease...for the time being...tat's enough...call tat simple life =)

yup it's for u...

HAPPY BIRTHDAY mummy!

eh, tried putting in ur pic....but i'm not IT savvy...sorri...=)...next time, i'll try to put all of us in k...haha...anyway tink i hav lots of our pics not given to me leh....sobsob....i'll wait....

just saw yappy's one week ago blog...yah something tat i wanted to voice out badly...so the following are personal subjective views...shun if u tink u r goin to be offended...but i dun tink i'll offend u hehe ^_*

ok beverly expected cannot make it any further...seems tat not many like her...i'm neutral towards her...so it doesn't matter she stays or not...den next came jeassea...yah maybe tat nite she hasn't been able to attract the votes enough for her to stay on...and tat shocked every1...and my sis commented...there's nothing to watch for in singapore idol anymore...sounds a bit true...and candice actually dropped out...for wat reason i'm still clueless....probably it's her studies....well, a waste....

then the spectacular 9....i felt so sad for DAVID...he may not have improved much but he's definitely better than some others....obviously, christopher wasn't up to any standard, and i dun find him any attractive either!!!! rather so-so or weak performances for the first few...until olinda...and gradually the rest seems to stand out as well...i tink i've been switching here and there as my fave...haha....actually i oso can't make up my mind previously who i'll support till the end....but thru the rock and roll nite...i've targeted SYLVESTER!!!...a cool guy....with a great voice (that really captivates me and i'm hoping for the same thing tonite) and personality...yah he's the one...i'll support till the end =)...MAIA is another one...but i dun feel her improving compared to others, so i'm very worried for her...my black list are christopher (as critize earlier oredi), daphne--juz never like her ever since the show started...the rest juz let them be....anyway those who r expected to be eliminated yet still in there, i've such a strong feeling tat it's all bcos they r christians!!!....and their church mates r crazily voting for them....cos how can it be possible tat sun ho's album always get the best sales....IMPOSSIBLE!!!! yup i'm getting a bit anti-christians here...so, sorri =\

waiting for tonite's show....and i hope christopher will get out!!!!!....eh better get back to serious work....=)

haiz...terrible feeling...
my mum still objects no matter wat...and kept saying all the things tat will make me sway...wth...
how many times hav tis happened......really can't take it anymore...
there r some things to say but it's getting late...i shall put it up in the next few days...

hey ppl...coming up is my 1 week break...but i'm afraid i may not be ard for the rest of next week...depends on situation...those i hav 'dates' wif so sorri...if u really need to contact me call or msg 98468868...k? take care ppl...

yah slackin away again...

where hav i heard b4 tat bloggin is actually addictive??? i dun feel tis way at all, writing in diary is even more addictive...=p...even got ur own handwriting to read next time...

ok, i'm juz trying to crap sth out...cos i'm stuck wif words...=\

is it better to start the day off happily and end it sadly?? or start the day off feeling depressed and end it happily?...i guess i'll choose the later one, cos u would need to have the energy to be depressed, and slp wif a smile is better i guess...

fingers not quite cooperating today...and for stupid reason, had a mouth fight, a shower wif tears...stress cannot be accumulated!! so if someday, u feel stressed better relieve yourself. the exam was ok, felt a bit cold though due to the air-conditioning. wif mistakes here n there, answering of qn wrongly, can only pray for a merit...

msg mum sorry...it's the only thing i could do at tat point of time.

had lunch wif sis at clementi, den suddenly tot of nus ppl, shld hav ask whether mummy, jy n sisi free or not...hmm..

slept thru the late afternoon.
went tuition and spent the first 15 min looking thru wat to give him do later on...and he, trying to draw pics on a piece of paper as a teacher's day card =)
and he has shown some improvement for last week CA, however, i still feel he can do better...hopefully he will.

tat's all i hav to say, i'm still a bit tired now...but dun tink will slp early haha...wanna watch a new variety show of jacky wu...but tonite, i muz slp comfortably on my bed...can't bear to leave tis bed, actually it's mattress not bed...cos hav gotten a sofa bed, which will be here tml...ya excited, but she bu de as well...=p

Jaa~~

yup tml is the day tat'll end my 'misery'...how long hav i been waiting for it to cum and finally go off...i'll be ever relieved right after tat. so i'm goin to catch a good slp now, wake up promptly tml, touch the keyboard a few more times b4 i set off for the somehow ulu place...once and for all, i still pray for a distinction =p

finally done wif ppt and my gonna-shorten-it essay...get sth done le, relief =)

finally get to eat katong laksa today, ever since tat drama series on chn 8 abt laksa, i've been yearning for it...so many mths hav passed and i finally got to eat it keke...muz scout for the nearest branch when i'm free otherwise can only wait for dad to drive down there...

will keep it short cos wan to watch tv...=p

last thing, thx dinko...for telling me the results...china won over russia....sad though....but anyway will still watch for the match later after midnite i guess...today is the last day to view any events le...haha

Ciao!

hmm...quite a happy day afterall...watched one of the vball semifinals...russia vs brazil...actually i dun really hav a fav team...it was during tat game tat i realised how much i wanted russia to win and they did marvellously =)...so i gonna catch the finals, guess will support them all the way liao...yah anyway russia team has tis super tall woman nearing 2m, and she actually looks like 933 DJ liyi...at least to me, but my sis said liyi is prettier instead...hahz...watever

supposedly to accompany yiwen so tat she wasn't so tense up by the injection, yet i did not help much except to sit at the medical centre and watched olympics...paiseh hor, =p

and wat a lecture i had today...my only lesson and i wasn't able to concentrate at all...there r basically 2 reasons for y i wouldn't concentrate: either talking away or napping...so today talking away happily...haha...wonder ppl behind me were disrupted by it =p...maybe i shall stop going for the lect, others oso skipped it...den i can get 2 full days (thur and fri) to really study...hmm...i shall consider about tat possibility...

hmm gotta go do chi-eng translation liao 
good niteZ!

i've always tot stress is sth tat will nvr happen to me...and indeed i nvr felt so in my life, cos i noe my limits...but for now, i'm pondering, do i really noe my limits???cos for the first time of my life, i am stressed..............are my expectations too high??? or wat has gone wrong??? i need time, need a life, need the freedom to do watever i like at any point of time without worrying about any other things...but somehow it's greatly impossible to have it at all.........and i guess i'm a different me now...changes tat don't seem too good...i hope to see a better me, and i wun get stress in tat me....so pardon me, if i'm harsher nowadays...

until i'm not feeling so stressed anymore, pls bear wif me!

break now...not fully utilising it...can see rite??haha...juz finished a brilliant presentation by my groupmates, yah it was brilliant probably except my part...hehz...so tend to slack...and again i was late for class early in the morning...forever...damn...really cannot take up 8.30 class le...or maybe i should start to change my sleeping habits...=p...juz feel like lazing ard...i should get a nap actually so tat i wun fall asleep later on during the seminar class...i've sort of experimented it...haha if i did get a nap, i really wun fall aslp in the class later on...tat happened for last week and all the previous weeks tat i din't do tat, i would be tired from hearing the tutor and...'knocked out'....=p....bad i noe, but heng i'm not the only one wif tis kind of bad habit...glad to hav somebody in the same boat wif me...kekeke...

now hav to start tinking wat's the common topic for marketing, accounting and banking n finance...something interested will be better...but seems hard though....i welcum all ideas and suggestions....or hope i'll get the inspiration soon....=p

tis oso not bad ya....*_^

phew seems to be a long day...=p

supposed to only hav a 2hr lect during the noon, but went sch b4 tat for a presentation discussion which made all of us a bit headache sia...even if they weren't, i was having literally headache....couldn't tink straight of wat they were saying hahz...den went for the lect, today is definitely not my day...sat at a not-so-good seat, and kana by the lecturer...oh so damn...it isn't very advisable to stand up from the seats lor, cos limited place ard u, haiz...and for god's sake, i'm wearing a skirt and it's not the long type...hj dear pls dun ever find me such a bad seat le...nvm in the future i'll go get the seats k?!?!? after tat went back to the same place for another presentation discussion...tis one more fruitful to me hahz...cos i got read up and do the tut, so at least can understand much much more and it really seem very effective for a group of ppl to get together and discuss the answers...and it's really discussing...can't remember tat i ever had tat kind of discussion which really seem effective to me for the past of my life...haha...maybe shld get more of tat kind of discussion...keke but not at such an off timing...sleepy timing i mean ^_^...yah practically the whole day passed like tat.....

and while i was a bit rushing for time, waited for several 179 until i could get on one...hmm...no choice, unavoidable...saw a fren's fren, managed to 'say hi' to each other...a bit awkward though, cos i juz stood a distance away and he seemed to want to chat...you yuan zai jian lor...=p

muz get some sleep le, another long day tml...haiz....tis week gonna be tiring....

tot i could make use of this afternoon free time to catch up some studies...but yah the usual self revealed again by slacking on the sofa watching k-drama, nap a little and watch table-tennis match...exciting, li jia wei should have been able to win...sad sad...and tat korean women couldn't keep her mouth shut sia...=p...the match reminded me of a volleyball match i watched days ago...china vs cuba (women team)...oso even out, fighting for the last set...only preliminary round lor hahz...but was so late oredi tat during the last set i actually fell into slp, woke up it was another game oredi....till now still dunno it's actually china or cuba won tat match...still find vball as my fave =) although i rarely get to even touch the ball...how i wish i was back to the younger dayz where i get all the chance i had to play vball, netball....haiz...y did i like those sports tat involve a team...if it only involves myself, i wouldn't hav to keep all the urges to play my fave sport inside me all the time...someday will bie1 chu1 bing4 haha....

bought i-weekly yesterday cos it's jay on the cover, a shot tat i dun really like it alot, not shuai enuff i guess haha...it seems tat he gonna hav his concert in nov...hmm...sure go...but the only thing is i wanna sit as front as possible...muz keep a lookout when the tix r really out for sale...=)

met jeremy days ago too...it was ard 11 pm??...yah should be lah, took 199 out from sch to go home u see...and he got on the bus at one of the stops in jurong west area...so he was actually seeing his gf home...eh maybe jea u noe who she is??haha...huiwen was wif me...so the 3 of us went home together...and i guess both of them did most of the toking, not unusual rite?? keke...tink he has changed a bit character-wise...juz a feelin la, from the way he said things...and the next day he msged me n asked, did i mind he got my number from annie(cos they often go out together)...i was like, huh, u oredi got my number, den u asked?? hahz...hope can go out wif him someday, he said he is sian in sch now haha, but of cos wif others too....definitely not juz me and him, tat would be wierd keke....

kk...hope i wun need to cum in once a week or so, there seems to be a lot of things waiting for me to get them done...i muz work hard tml...which is actually today...sunday....nan de i would be at home the whole day....muz really make good use of it...i hope i can....Nitezzz =)

i juz like it big big can see clearly =), it's definitely not an eyesore k!!!

having AB213 tut now...was late cos woke up late =p hence get to sit at the last row, and the class is in IT lab...hehz...learning to input endnote which i nvr came upon...yah he was blabbering away, i juz sometimes pay some attention...and try doing wat he said...afterall the words on the screen r so small...and he would nvr call for me for demo...hahz, advantage of not having an english name =)...used to hate tis tutor and yet now i'm starting to feel neutral towards him...he isn't too bad after all maybe as a tutor...but definitely not as a lecturer =p

yah i actually woke up at 7.30 tis morning for a 8.30 class...having 2 full days consecutively is kind of tiring, no time for other stuffs le even my piano...the only days i can touch it is like one or two days per week and tat definitely wun help at all...sort out my tots finally, and really need to buck up le, no time to waste...cos my tut and readings r laggin and presentations finally r all comin up...so r the quizzes...really hav the bad feeling tat tis sem wun be any good...heng got a ex-tut mate's motivation...i feel more motivated now hahz...oops tat doesn't mean tat i can't attend tut w/o paying attention keke...

ok guess tat shall be all for now, tut ending in another haf hour...i better stop *_*

thank to all...
i guess i'm starting to see a small spot of light from afar...
i shall keep walking towards there, till my world is full of brightness...
gotta pack all the unhappy things away...
gotta pick up where i left off...
yah life is full of lessons to be learnt...
another lesson i've learnt...
face reality...
one's power is too insignificant to even change reality...
but you will be able to overcome it no matter what...

hav to revert back to my style of writing...tis is juz not me...hmm...i'll in the next blog.

hmm...almost feel tat i could break down at any point of time...ppl, do start praying for me, hoping tat everything will be over very soon, i would then be able to lead a peaceful and calm life...no, it's not family prob dun worry...and definitely not r/s...juz some unpleasant thing tat i really dun wan to tok abt it...i can only wait for better dayz to cum now, nothin much i could do actually...all cos of my stupidness...haiz...i noe i shouldn't be too bothered by it but juz can't help feeling tat i'm living like hell...cos of all these, no mood to study, do tut, gonna lag behind and gonna waste my tis sem of studying...disappointed at myself, sorry for my parents tat they actually have such a daughter..........
guess everybody has their little stories hidden in them, i'm juz one of them...nothin beats frenship, it's the best thing tat one could ever own...somewhere i heard from....frenz are actually your siblings god forgot to give u....i'm glad both of u r there for me to help me thru THX! 
life seem aimless now...there's nothin i'm lookin forward to...but i now i'll hav to stop tis and pick up the life tat really belongs to me...i will.

not in very good mood nowadays...pi qi bu hao...den sometimes unpleasant things happened at home...actually it's juz btw parents mostly and mum scolding ard...tink all these has pathed out the road to my phobia of me getting like her...as a wife and as a mother...it's too early to tink of all these...but it's really something tat i wouldn't wan it happen to me....haiz...guess i'm getting yu wu lun ci, dun be bothered...

yah the chalet i had a week ago...well well, heng wasn't arrow to get drunk...anyway tat's the only time in my life tat i was awake for about 30hours?!?!? and so i slept thru my 2hrs lect when i got back to sch on sat =p...the lect supposed to be fun cos once in a while laughters woke me up...but i did compensate during the following tutorial on mon by paying full attention =) and it's enjoyable...tat's one of my electives...the other elective juz attended first lesson yesterday...tink i gonna flunk it...choose the wrong one le...no idea wat the lecturer cum tutor was toking abt at all...maybe gotta go consult mummy le...help in chinese!!!

these few days sure will quarrel wif mum again...haiz...she better stops grumbling at me....-_-

tis month's pocket really burnt a big hole le...haiz...now den understand y i should have work during the hols...books to me cost a bomb...gotta pay for upcoming chalet...print notes (cos lotz of pages...at least to me it seem so =p)...and i dun forget to eat for sure...=p

today finally did sit attentively for lect...hahz...maybe bcos able to discuss the content wif frenz if there's anything we dun understand...extended fmaths content mah...and my frenz r my jc classmates as well...phew...so felt a little sense of achievement hahz...i'm really such a rong yi man zu de ren...

looking forward to tml's chalet...can eat bbq food, can play, have fun for the last nite?? b4 really start moving wif sch work...oh yah it's actually the orientation camp og ppl having chalet...and to tink tat the juniors actually made something for all the seniors...very happy...it's a baby sock wif personalized name and sweets, lollipops...cutie...=)...this made me tink back of the old sec dayz as peer support leader...tat's the best time of life...juniors really can make u feel great hahz, rite jea??

tink i'm getting somewhere in life...at least not standing in the old spot waiting for nothing =)...hope tis kind of feeling will keep rolling in =)

cool concert last nite!!! FIR put up a great and 'high' performance...something i can't resist so if they gonna hold a concert in singapore, i wun miss tat out!! it lasted abt 1 hour wif 8 songs from their album (tat's quite alot) and other songs, bits and pieces...the only regret i had was...not getting there early to queue for admission into the auditorium...so got myself seats in the upper aisle...up there quite dangerous lor, so nobody stand, and audiences below were enjoying themselves so much...the feeling of wanting to get 'high' was restricted...i regret...i regret...haiz...but get to watch them live in action was the consolation =)...their 'live' gong li very zai...F.I.R. rocks!

yesterday class made me feel a bit pressured...cos there r quite alot of yr3's in tat class...tat's juz y i feel tis way...but there's oso quite a number of yr2's...a bit scary though...wonder can make it thru tis sem...cos suddenly dun seem to noe wat i'm doing or rather studying abt...haiz...gotta start to mentally push myself le...

ntu's flag day today, thus no sch...spent my day juz like any other days during the hols...haiz...not in the mood of sch starting yet lah...

am a true slacker!!

erm...happy thing today is tat i managed to get hold of the FIR concert tix =)...all thx to a great pal hehz...he let me cut queue..opps...bo bian it was such a long queue an hr b4 the actual distributing time...=p...i did queue myself b4 cutting queue, cos he came and brought me to his queue...otherwise tink i would still be able to get?!?!?maybe but will be damn late for lect...so wanna be punctual for lect, hav to go to the front a bit lor =)

unhappy things erm...couldn't concentrate during lect =p haiz...not a good start...wanna go lib print notes and tut, sianz cos another long queue for the printers...wanna go bookshop buy books oso sianz cos long queue again, but tis queue moving rather fast however most of the books seem to be out of stock oredi...no point...met karsze there...yah everybody hecticly buying textbooks...den so disappointed, only received a 'thx' from yingbin cos i expected more than tat...but ever since tat fateful day, nothin more than a sentence from him bah =p nvm...and one last thing saw a person tat i dun wan to see at all...damn! gonna seem hard not to see him ard, oso dunno y dun wan to see his face appearing in front of me oso...haiz...

getting tired...Nitez!

tot i was juz back at perak...now i'm oredi back here in sg...Haiz

pretty easy life while back at perak (my birth place in case u dunno keke) although did nothin much except to eat...cos grandma will always cook 'hao liao' if anybody went back...so putting on more weight again...and playin, bridging r/s wif my cousins...can only see them those rare few times a year...also got to see certain unpleasant happenings back there...cos my grandparents living wif jiujiu and daughter-in-law...so unavoidably, there r conflicts...and...aiya lotz of things...juz better keep it in heart...tat's y i've always been tinking, when i start to work, i would like to bring my grandparents to live wif us...but grandma has diabetes and she has to take injection everyday and of cos medication...am i capable of looking after her???haiz...
paiseh!!! to ppl who contacted me during those few days while i was away...tot could use my jiujiu's internet at home, but he has shifted his com to his new shop le...and i din't really have time to go to the really nearby cybersurf shop...keke...yah it's not a cafe...hahz...but i did go on the last day over there, and to my ultimate shock...network is damn slow...slow till i tot the com could hang any moment...and almost fell asleep while waiting for the sites to load lor...cannot make it...

the last few days been nua-ing at home...really dun feel like moving out of the house...so kept myself in home watch vcd again...it's korean drama again =)...about teacher-student love...now showing on chn 8 la...the teacher got dimples very shuai hahz...mi si ren le...yupz more shuai den tat PE teacher mr Potassium Hydroxide keke =p

tml sch starting....3mths has been over...since it's over, no use tinking back of wat i've or hav not done over tat 3mths...hope it'll be a great start tml...it better be or else gonna blame yingbin(reminding me of how to lose a guy in 10 days ^_^)...hahz...bo bian his bday tml...probably the first thing i gonna do tml is to queue for FIR campus concert tix...hehz...cos u all noe la i'm so into them nowadays...so happy tat they actually havin campus concert in my sch!!! hope i'll get the tix!!! otherwise i would be very sad...

so gonna end the nite now and wake up tml wif a great start =)

wat a day...

not i wan to grumble but the weather was really playing wif me today! it started to rain quite early in the morn, so i went to bring in the clothes, close the windows (hav to otherwise can flood my house...not tat serious lah hahz)...and within minutes the sun was out, so the waiting-to-dry clothes were out, windows opened...okay and tis cycle continued thruout the morn till mid afternoon...erm...therefore i oso can't keep track of how many times i went to bring in and out the clothes plus the opening and closing of the windows...fun hor...haiz

and the other thing, bro got fever...tot he would be okay after taking medicine early in the morn b4 mum went to work...unfortunately, the fever kept running till almost 40degree celsius...and got him into a headache...nobody's home except me...wan to bring him down to see doc, he said he couldn't walk to there, energy-less...so kept calling mum and dad...finally old neighbour came to rescue, drove me and my bro to the clinic...but after seeing doc, seem of no help...he din't get any better...all i can do for him today is to cook porridge to let him eat...gave him medicine and lots of water...he muz be feeling damn terrible...haiz...tink he wun be fine tml as well, so gotta stay home to look after him...can't go for lunch wif classmates le...nvm...luckily i'm still having hols and not working can stay home look after him...
